21/22 SKIS ARE HERE. Little bit of everything for everyone. From park to all-mountain we cover it all. Get a taste of 21/22 Skis now! 🔗 in bio. 

What better way to break in our new marketing guy @jake.nomiddlename.dube than make him go live with some athletes and our head of ski engineering @peterforscale! Questions on the new lineup message us whenever! 🚨

The LINE Vision 98 shares the same build and featherweight feel as the Vision 108 and 118, straight down to the THC Technology. Whether you're looking to rally through the freshies, arc on groomers, or even motor skin-tracks, the Vision 98 is up to the task. The 98mm waist footprint offers versatility for those days that you don't need the float. 

It may be one of the lightest skis you'll get your hands on, but don't let that fool you, the Vision 98 will rip whatever you throw at it.

Link in biø to learn more. 

#LINEskis #Skiingisbelieving #Morefunner

Link in biø to learn more and grab your new powder weapon. 

#LINEsksi #skiingisbelieving #Morefunner

Our freestyle team's favorite ski, the LINE Blend, has been redesigned for the 2020/2021 season. Same buttery LINE Blend flex, same Blend feel, certified and approved by Will Wesson himself. So what's changed? We've blunted the tip for locking in those nose blocks, we've extended the sidecut for quicker turning, and we've widened the tip & tail for more surface area to press on deep into your butters. 

Link in biø to learn more and gear up. 

#LINEskis #Morefunner #LINEblend #Bendyourblends

Created with THC Technology, a featherweight chassis paired with a responsive core allows the Vision to be unlike anything you've ever skied.

Smash the link in biø to learn more 👆

#LINEskis #LINEvision #Skiingisbelieving #Morefunner

Link in biø to learn more about the new #lineTWpro. 

#LINEskis #Morefunner

🔗 in biø to see all 21/22 Skis NOW LIVE on our brand new website, poles, skis, and more! 👀 🥵 🤤

The 🆕 21/22 #LINEvision Collection - you’re going to hold this ski in your hands and when you feel how light it is your brain will malfunction. 😊

When a ski is too light, it’s unstable, and when stable, it’s too heavy. A design solution was needed, enter THC Construction. No not just an excuse to make a pot reference, it’s low weight, strength, and durability like you’ve never felt described in # form. #SkiingIsBelieving 

#LINEskis #MoreFunner #AlmostWinter

node.text:
The 🆕 21/22 #LINEsirfrancisbacon and #LINEoutline arent magic. Though it damn well feels like it on snow. 😳

These skis make up our Convex collection. The result of some of the biggest breakthroughs from LINE engineers to properly bring 3D convex tips & tails to the mountain. This tech creates a looser feel in soft snow which allows a ski with a deep sidecut to not be hooky at speed while still allowing maximum edge hold on hardpack. 👍

#LINEskis #MoreFunner #MakeYourOwnPath

STILL SKIING. 🚨 After a winter season comes to a close the sadness settles in…

Good to know it doesn’t have to! Many of you, as well as our athletes, have decided there’s no reason for their season to truly end. With many spectacular year-round skiing destinations across the globe we wanted to highlight a few in our North American back yard the LINE team has descended upon, LINE Summer Recap 🔗 in biø!
